<br>
You could do it solo like this:<br>
<br>
1. Pull with malosi.<br>
<br>
2. Use a swollen fungusbeast gland from FG or that ball o' string thing to snare him.<br>
<br>
3. Shoot off scars of sigil at him and drag him around while you have an expedience'd water pet behind him, backstabbing away.<br>
<br>
4. Just keep doing that until he dies.<br>
<br>
The safer way would to have your local friendly druid snare him for you, but if you're doing it solo I'd recommend that. Or just chain cast away at him.<br>
