<br>
1.  Got KEI.<br>
2.  Summoned Earth Pet. (Voc_Earth)<br>
3.  Gave it Summoned Armor, Burnout, and Expedience.<br>
4.  In my experience chain-petting is more efficiant than nuking Slixin due to his extreme hitpoints.  So, instead of nuking, I just chain cast my pet (earth was best, because he kept Slixin rooted while I was casting another pet, and while medding.)  <br>
5.  DS the new pet.<br>
6.  I would run out of mana while Slixin was at 1% health (he doesn't run, but he gets slower.)  Then I would just run around and sit occasionally while mana regenerated.<br>
7.  If I remember right, it took about 8 pets to take him down.  And I had to kill slixin about 5 times before he droped the piece. <p><BR>
