<br>
He is lv 50, has about 15000 hp and hits for about 130, but not all that often. Being a lv 60, I would expect a magician could take him down with one pet and nuking like hell. It is, however, far more interesting that by chain petting a magician can take him down at lv 51-2. It is still dicy, and you may get into trubble, but you can <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
The only nuke you should use is the lowest bolt you can find in your book. You should pull to a pet parked to the south of the crater. I have yet to see anything there that isn't pulled there. You have to malosi, because the root from the pet MUST stick. And then just chain pet untill he is down.<br>
<br>
He is on a 22 min spawn, leaving plenty of time to med back up (BOOOORING)<br>
<br>
But soloable? Definitely!<br>
